WEBVTT

00:01.604 --> 00:03.438
Harris:
<i>It's called Lewy Body.</i>

00:03.440 --> 00:06.742
<i>Degenerative progression</i>
<i>is slow, irreversible,</i>

00:06.744 --> 00:08.943
<i>and there is no known cure.</i>

00:08.946 --> 00:11.414
Dr. Harris, I'm a reporter.

00:11.416 --> 00:13.182
I think there may be
<i>some information here</i>

00:13.184 --> 00:15.918
<i>that could be of serious</i>
<i>interest to the public.</i>

00:15.920 --> 00:18.553
I'm here to discuss
your relocation.

00:18.555 --> 00:20.188
<i>This is not a request.</i>

00:20.190 --> 00:21.589
I want you
to run for governor

00:21.591 --> 00:23.958
<i>against Mac Cullen</i>
<i>in the primary.</i>

00:23.960 --> 00:26.293
Ben, primaries are four days away.
Are you focusing?

00:26.295 --> 00:28.562
I am, on you.
I need to see you.

00:28.564 --> 00:33.399
Man: <i>We are projecting</i>
<i>a win for Ben Zajac.</i>

00:33.401 --> 00:35.968
We won!

00:35.970 --> 00:38.238
Kane has changed.
We don't act now,

00:38.240 --> 00:41.441
we may lose the opportunity of
both our political lifetimes.

00:41.443 --> 00:42.710
Change is in the air.

00:42.712 --> 00:44.745
<i>We have to</i>
<i>realign ourselves.</i>

00:44.747 --> 00:46.114
Do you have what it takes?

00:46.116 --> 00:48.416
I want names.
Who?!

00:48.418 --> 00:50.886
Tom: <i>Every person who has</i>
<i>plotted against me</i>

00:50.888 --> 00:53.922
<i>will feel the force</i>
<i>of my wrath.</i>

00:53.924 --> 00:57.025
<i>No one will be</i>
<i>left unscathed.</i>

00:57.027 --> 01:00.096
- <i>Police!</i>
- Tom: <i>Why did you do it?</i>

01:00.098 --> 01:02.932
The only end that matters
to you now is you.

01:02.934 --> 01:05.001
I can't abide by that.

01:05.003 --> 01:07.870
- Tom: <i>What would</i> <i>you advise I do now...</i>
- <i>( Gunshot )</i>

01:07.872 --> 01:10.572
<i>...given I know</i>
<i>what you've done?</i>

01:10.574 --> 01:13.509
You will have to choose
where you stand.

01:13.511 --> 01:17.279
<i>It will be up to you</i>
<i>to prove your commitment.</i>

01:17.281 --> 01:19.148
( crying )
Tom.

